snippet: Branden Grace won his fourth European Tour event of the season with a two-shot victory over Thorbjorn Olesen in the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship.
abstract: Branden Grace wins the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship golf tournament, his fourth European Tour event of the season.
lead_paragraph: Branden Grace won his fourth European Tour event of the season with a two-shot victory over Thorbjorn Olesen in the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship.

headline.seo: Branden Grace Wins at Dunhill Links Championship
